Package: metadynminer
Type: Package
Title: Metadynminer reads, analyses and visualizes metadynamics HILLS files from Plumed
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2018-08-14
Author: Vojtech Spiwok [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Vojtech Spiwok <spiwokv@vscht.cz>
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Description: Metadynminer reads 1D and 2D metadynamics HILLS files from Plumed package (1).
  It uses a fast algorithm (2) to claculate the free energy surface from hills. Minima can
  be located and ploted on free energy surfaces.
References:
  1. Tribello G.A. et al. Comput. Phys. Commun. 2004, 185 604-613.
  2. Hosek P., Spiwok V. Comput. Phys. Commun. 2016, 198 222-229.
LazyData: true
License: GPL-3
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
